div.div:
0: push first line of change to new branch + create draft PR
1: mark PR as ready for review
2: after QC mirror the branch into a transport in DEV(decision point)
abaplint.app informs on parallel changes
3: release TOC to TST(pass information back to the PR)
4: more QC in TST
5: more changes, developer pushes to branch, another TOC(flow screen ensures system and branch matches)
6: release the TR, /SDF/SEQUENCE_CHECK, it goes to production, branch can be merged(and deleted)

switch.text: 0: push first line of change to new branch + create draft PR...
